<p><hi rend="italic">Gardeners’ Chronicle</hi> has reprinted THH’s <hi rend="italic">Times</hi> review.</p>  
<p>W. H. Harvey made weak attack on <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> [<hi rend="italic">Gard. Chron.</hi> (1860): 145–6], to which Hooker made admirable rejoinder [<hi rend="italic">Gard. Chron.</hi> (1860): 170–1].</p> 
